 menu and download the app please visit http://www.fooda.com/ssbeastatrium . Click the calendar on the top left of the page for the menu for each day of the week. Come visit Fooda at the first floor east atrium of SSB.  Designed to meet the nutritional needs and the environmental expectations of University students, faculty, staff and visitors.  Regular Hours   Monday-Friday 11:00am – 1:30pm  Saturday & Sunday Closed  Spring Break Hours  3/16/20 – 3/20/20 Monday – Friday 11:00am – 1:30pm  3/23/20 – 3/29/20 Closed  Resume Regular Hours 3/30/20           Dining    Back to main content           Student Center East    Student Center West    Student Services Building    Alternate Campus Dining                  UIC Logo        Student Centers         Quick Links    Staff Directory    Student Employment    Feedback      Resources    Lockers Info and Policy    Bicycle Repair    Donation Bins      Tools    Building Directory    BM Reports    Operations Reports        BUTTON    Policies    Sustainability    Hours & Locations         Contact   scenters@uic.edu        Social Media Accounts    Facebook    Twitter    Instagram    YouTube             UIC.edu links   UIC.edu  Academic Calendar  Athletics  Campus Directory  Disability Resources  Emergency Information  Event Calendar  Job Openings  Library  Maps  UIC Safe Mobile App  UIC Today  UI Health  Veterans Affairs        Powered by Red 2.38.0  © 2020 The Board of Trustees of the University of Illinois |  Privacy Statement    Campuses   University of Illinois System  Urbana-Champaign  Springfield      Cookie Settings                 